text: Final Analysis is an American 1992 melodrama thriller movie. It is about seduction, lies, manipulation and murders. Uma Thurman stars as Diana Baylor and Kim Basinger stars as Heather Evans. The movie got mixed to negative reviews. Final Analysis was released in February of 1992. The box office performance was very poor. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox.
